title: Manson woman shot in head
content:
MANSON, Wash. - The Chelan County Sheriff's Office is investigating an case where a woman was found in a Manson home with a gunshot wound to the head.
Deputies responded to a home at 3 am Thursday and found the 23-year-old victim with a single gunshot wound to the head. They were able to get her airlifted from the scene to an area hospital.
Her current condition is not known.
Detectives are continuing to investigate the incident and have not released any additional information.
